## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of sources that specifically address how the world views Christians. Most sources focus on defining the Christian worldview from an internal perspective rather than providing an external analysis. Additionally, the lack of recent data and diverse geographical perspectives may limit the comprehensiveness of the findings. Further research could include surveys and studies that explore non-Christian perspectives on Christianity globally.

